EXPANDED BRIEF:
${expandedBrief}

WEBSITE TYPE: ${websiteType}
VIBE: ${vibe}
SECTIONS TO CREATE: ${sections.join(', ')}

Generate comprehensive, professional content in this exact JSON structure:
${jsonSchema}

CRITICAL REQUIREMENTS:
âœ… Write RICH, DETAILED content - minimum 200 words for about section
âœ… Make it sound ${vibe} in tone throughout
âœ… Use professional, engaging copy that converts visitors
âœ… Include specific details, benefits, and value propositions
âœ… Make testimonials authentic with specific results
âœ… Create compelling, action-oriented headlines
âœ… Use emojis that match the ${vibe} vibe
âœ… Provide VERY SPECIFIC image search terms (not generic)
âœ… Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown formatting, no extra text

Remember: Quality over quantity - make every word count!`;

